Company Overview of New York Life Investment Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
New York Life Investment Management LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals. It also caters to investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, corporations, and insurance companies. The firm manages separate client focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It also launched and manages equity, fixed income, balanced, and multi-asset mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in the alternative investments markets. For the equity portion of its portfolio, the firm invests in the growth and value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-c...
New York Life Investment Management LLC is a privately owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to individuals. It also caters to investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, corporations, and insurance companies. The firm manages separate client focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. It also launched and manages equity, fixed income, balanced, and multi-asset mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in the alternative investments markets. For the equity portion of its portfolio, the firm invests in the growth and value stocks of small-cap, mid-cap, and large-cap companies. For the fixed income portion of its portfolios, it invests in high-yield bonds, index bonds, corporate investment-grade bonds, convertible securities, government bonds, and money market instruments. For its alternative investments, the firm provides hedge fund portfolios, private equity portfolios, private finance portfolios, and real estate portfolios, which include debt, equity, mezzanine, and REIT equities. It obtains external research to create its portfolio. The firm was founded in April 2000 and is based in New York City with additional offices in Atlanta, Georgia, Chicago, Illinois, Plano, Texas, Parsippany, New Jersey, San Francisco, California, Westwood, Massachusetts, Monterrey, Mexico, and London, United Kingdom. New York Life Investment Management LLC operates as a subsidiary of New York Life Investment Management Holdings LLC.
